0000EDr 2               famistudio_chn_epsm_trigger:       .res FAMISTUDIO_EXP_EPSM_FM_CHN_CNT + FAMISTUDIO_EXP_EPSM_RHYTHM_CNT ; bit 0 = new note triggered, bit 7 = note released.
0000EDr 2               .endif
